original_title: WHAT THE FUCK IS GOING ON BETWEEN US, FUCK?
overview: During their training together, Lola makes no secret of her supposed dislike and tries to hide her feelings from the rest of the team. But with her behaviour she shoots herself straight into the ground. Has she now lost her chances with Zoe forever or is there still a way?
title: WHAT THE FUCK IS GOING ON BETWEEN US, FUCK?
